title: Gross domestic product ( GDP ) per capita in the United States 2024
yAxis: GDP per capita in U.S. dollars
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes GDP per capita in U.S. dollars. In total the number of data points it has is 41.
Overall GDP per capita in U.S. dollars has increased over the Year.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2017 and 2018.
The highest GDP per capita in U.S. dollars, of value 76252.11 was reached at Year 2024
The lowest GDP per capita in U.S. dollars, of value 17086.44 was reported at Year 1984
